\begin_inset Formula $u_{t}$
\end_inset

.
 This law of motion has a steady state solution at 
\begin_inset Formula $x=0$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $u=1$
\end_inset

.
 We replace the choice of 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{t}$
\end_inset

